{"tid":1152401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖記新衫輸波 C朗諷敵將矮小後道歉","createTime":"2019-05-13T02:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T06:22:43.000Z","uid":138762,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4b1130e676a7de67f99cae5f96a7850b39db1f","tid":1152401,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】換上新裝的祖雲達斯周日敗走羅馬，而球星基斯坦奴朗拿度嘲諷羅馬翼鋒費奧倫斯太矮小，隨即道歉。<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯周日在聯賽作客以0:2不敵羅馬，球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）於58分鐘與羅馬球星費奧倫斯發生言語衝突，打手勢侮辱對方不夠高，並指：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">矮仔，你無資格跟我説話。</span></span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n費奧倫斯賽後談及矛盾的起源，「我們為對友得到治療，兩次暫停比賽，但他卻兩次繼續進攻。高拉洛夫上半場就放棄突擊的機會，這就是我們的質素。他是金球獎得主，以為自己甚麼都沒錯，還在場上胡言亂語。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，祖雲達斯周日首度披上來季主場球衣上陣，新波衫放棄傳統只有黑白直間，而是一半黑、一半白，中間加入了粉紅色直間，網友賽前已對新設計很不滿，紛紛在社交網站抗議，形容是史上最差的設計。如今新衫落場即落敗，也許會更招人批評。"},{"pid":"bec89502fd39e288d93a771ddaee42bc39354e93","tid":1152401,"uid":241774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"件衫點都好過啲倒模衫啦"},{"pid":"83e33f17ebf20c3491ec3af2ce8ec04a01c32225","tid":1152401,"uid":4661,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.malaymail.com/uploads/articles/2019/2019-05/as_roma_juve_1305.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.malaymail.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2F2019%2F2019-05%2Fas_roma_juve_1305.JPG&h=6704bcc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e659a93f46c9c7970733d643faad02f89993d67","tid":1152401,"uid":46849,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"他首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1e0ec8e92d1d9ceaeab5b92488858e21ba1a72","tid":1152401,"uid":143582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:11:39